Text: For those of you that are downloading this torrent, please be considerate and _seed_ _this_ _for_ _others_! I've been seeding this one for two weeks now, and I've yet to see the number of seeders reach 3. I have, however, seen more than 10 different peers download from me, and only 2 or 3 of them actually seeded for over a day (once they downloaded 100%).
